%% render.orientation: portrait
flowchart TD
  A[Protected form page render] --> B[Challenge service signs form proof]
  B --> C[Rendered form carries hidden token and hidden trap field]
  C --> D[Person completes sign-up membership request or report]
  D --> E[Submission reaches protected controller]
  E --> F{Proof valid and fresh?}
  F -->|No| G[Reject submission with validation error]
  F -->|Yes| H{Trap field empty and timing plausible?}
  H -->|No| G
  H -->|Yes| I{Nonce already used?}
  I -->|Yes| G
  I -->|No| J[Normal create path continues]
  J --> K[Request saved and reviewed through normal workflow]

